phrases: It sounds like she is been resurrected!
So Menma's come back to have her wish granted.
I think she is just my hallucination.
I blurted out everything about Menma in the heat of the moment,
but I did not expect him to accept everything so easily.
Like I told you, she is just my...
So you have been using this secret fort?
Yeah, but only when I am in Japan.
All of those red circles mark places that I have visited.
I wanted to see all kinds of different places in the world.
So I have been traveling using the money I saved from my part-time job.
I do not have time for that.
On my last trip I went to Southeast Asia.
He used to be tiny, and now he is gotten so huge.
And like this, and like that.
You have not changed, have you.
To take a cruise down to my jungle?
I wonder what is going to pop out...
Right, we are getting way off topic.
Did you make her some kind of promise?
I do not remember anything like that.
Did not she mention she wanted Desu Yo.'s autograph?
Do you really think she would rise from the grave for Desu Yo.?
What is wrong with you, Kurimaru?
I will give you some yogurt when we get home.
So Naruko, did you really go over to Yadomi's house?
Having to deal with a hikikomori must suck.
But, do not you feel that way sometimes?
You know, feeling like you do not want to do anything, not wanting to get out of bed in the morning.
Sometimes, I... actually, I often feel like that.
Yeah, I know what you mean.
But I do not want to be compared to that loser.
He is probably having a wet dream about you right now.
Looks like she is an Oodai student.
You should just ignore me during situations like these.
I would be embarrassed if anyone saw me talking to a girl from Mido High.
What do you mean by that?
I went out of my way to bring that to you!
I did not ask you to.
Since when were you so full of yourself?
You were always so timid as a kid.
And you have not changed at all.
You were always easily influenced by others.
Those girls look like they cannot keep their legs shut and you fit right in.
Even though you always used to imitate Meiko Honma.
Do not use a dead girl's name so lightly!
You still get upset when you say it yourself.
You like Menma, do not you?
If only I had not spurred them on like that.
Who would like an ugly girl like...
If I had not, then things would not have gone like that...
When the froggie croaks, it is time to go back.
Are you going to criticize a customer for what he buys?
How many years ago did that come out?
Please sell it to me if you have it.
I mean, sell it to me already!
But she just could not find it.
Now that you mention it, she did say something about Building Builder.
Is not that pricey for a game that came out five years ago?
I will have you know that that is a fair price.
There is a premium on this game since you cannot find it anywhere anymore.
Today I came up with a rather fabulous dish.
So we are having fried meat for dinner.
Let us see, how did it go...
Start off by picking one out of the three critters.
Menma still has not come back.
She is my stress manifesting itself as a hallucination.
She should not exist in the first place.
Just call me Poppo like in the old days.
You are being so cold, Yuki.
That is the first time anyone's called me that.
Menma's been resurrected over at Jintan's place.
Is he bringing that up again...
What is he saying about Menma?
I saw him again for the first time in a while.
He is as awesome as ever.
What is he saying about Menma?
He called her an auditory hallucination?
I am not too sure, but apparently Menma wants him to grant her wish.
You know Jintan, I tried to wash myself, but it just felt like air blowing at me.
You should pay a little more attention to the fact that you have matured.
Actually, you have not matured all that much in one place.
I get the feeling I have met you before.
I heard that you get it when you trade Nokemon using a cable.
It is leftovers from last night.
Well, I am off to work.
Have a- Have a safe trip.
That is right, I would completely forgotten.
Menma did say her wish cannot come true without everyone together.
Oh yeah, I saw an auditory hallucination, too.
Anyway, so that is what it was.
So we need to get our hands on another Nokemon game.
There is someone who might already have the game...
I hated my curly hair and glasses back then.
Anaru, let us get matching stickers!
I will give you one, too.
I really liked her, but I also really hated her.
Naruko, come down here for a bit.
You want me to play Nokemon?
What is wrong with acting like kids every once in a while?
I can see fine without them.
It is really been a long time since the two of you have come over.
Say, do you want to try the jelly Naruko made last night?
Do you still have some on Anaru's jelly left?
Anyway, getting the rare Nokemon is Menma's wish.
Idiot, I told you not to talk about that.
I mean, what was that about Menma?
It is like she is been popping up in my dreams...
Let us see, Nokemon should be...
No, those are my Love and Perry cards.
And that one's for Cow King.
We are looking for Nokemon, not Cow King.
Why have not you joined us in her room?
Because when I am around, both my mom and Anaru start feeling sad.
Are you actually looking for it?
You actually wrote your name on this little game?
You were really thorough back then.
I have not read it in a while.
I cannot believe it, why do not I have Poitto?
Like I said, you have to trade rare Nokemon like Poison or Gangarga...
You cannot find Poison in the field.
You have to evolve him from Poitto.
Let me see yours real quick.
Anaru has not changed after all.
She is kind, and she has lots of video games and manga.
She is the same as she was back then.
It helped me kill some time.
Do I get something for helping you?
Now we just connect the cable and...
Now I can trade with a friend.
It looks like that was not my wish.
But lots of nice things happened.
You are friends with Anaru and Poppo again.
All you think of are other people.
Lately, all I have done has all been fun.
'Lately all I have done has all been fun.'
This is the first time I have had fun in a while, too.
The weather's nice today, and I had fun all day...
It looks like my trauma is not going away any time soon.
But as long as there is a tomorrow,
I feel like I can take my time...
We do not accept credit cards.
Menma the Hero has found a Nokemon shop.
Buddy King the rare Nokemon has been born!

We met in an unexpected moment
when you called out to me at the crosswalk,
I might have hidden shyly behind my bag,
but the truth is, I was really, really happy.
The fireworks blossomed heartrendingly beautiful across the night sky,
and time passed as swiftly as the wind.
We shared so many happy times and trilling adventures
I will never forget the hopes and dreams we shared during that one summer's end.
I am sure we will meet again in another August, in maybe ten years time.
I could feel your heartfelt thanks all the way until the end.
And I know it must have been painful to hold back your tears and say goodbye with a smile.
But those are my best memories.
We still do not know the name of the flower we saw that day.

Upon pages and pages of entries
We have put down all our emotions
But now I have hit a writer's block
I do not know how to finish this page anymore
Putting a bookmark in my diary
You and I go out to ride the bike we found in the dumpster
Let us go to our secret place
Where we piled up our bricks of memories
Run up the hill, where we can see the horizon
Where we can see the sky so fearfully blue
With cider in my right hand
My other hand helps me search for you
You used to come find me way back when
You used to demand me of so much more
You are both still standing right by my side
Yet why do I pray to see you both again?
There must be something off with me
